<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.10">
<l>pulli vaṇṭaṟai yumpoḻil puṭaicūḻ teṉṉāli yirunta māyaṉai</l>
<l>kalliṉ maṉṉutiṇ ṭōḷkaliya ṉoliceyta</l>
<l>nalla viṉṉicai mālai nālumō raintumoṉ ṟumnaviṉṟu tāmuṭaṉ</l>
<l>valla rāyuraip pārkkiṭa mākum vāṉulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having learned these four, five, and one [verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">of this garland of sweet sounds</l>
<l>Composed of words by Kaliyaṉ, [his] strong arms which endure like stone,</l>
<l>About Māyaṉ who sits in Āli of the South encircled on [all] sides by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where honeybees hum, embracing,</l>
<l>For those who recite [them] altogether as masters,</l>
<l rend="indent">their place will be in the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
